description: Welcome to Home of Little Baos! Little Bao is a collection of 7777 Cute Dumplings called "Bao". Step into a world of culinary delight and heartwarming connections with Little Baos, a collection of 7777 adorable edible dumplings called "Bao" on the BASE blockchain. Inspired by the heartwarming tradition of sharing dumplings, Little Baos embody the essence of kindness and togetherness, inviting you to join a vibrant community that celebrates art, food, and giving back.
